358
00:38:04,520 --> 00:38:07,390
Komorník Fu ti dal kľúč?

359
00:38:07,390 --> 00:38:09,030
Kto iný?

360
00:38:10,900 --> 00:38:14,400
Ale nemaj to tým dvom za zlé,

361
00:38:14,400 --> 00:38:17,440
Ja som zástupkyňa Tian Ji. Ak CEO odchádza,

362
00:38:17,440 --> 00:38:20,360
